data.description: Welcome to this STUNNING corner lot property ideal for a multi-generational family unit. This spacious home features 6 bedrooms, including a convenient downstairs bedroom with its own en suite bathroom. The main upstairs bedroom offers a GRAND experience with a large en suite bathroom, perfect for relaxation & privacy. Additionally, there are 4 bedrooms upstairs, 2 which have en suite facilities. Also there is a detached BRAND NEW 3-bedroom guest house or in-law quarters, providing potential RENTAL INCOME or space for extended family members. Only minutes away, you can explore the beauty of Rainbow River & enjoy the amenities of Rainbow Springs State Park. As an added bonus, there is an option to purchase the neighboring side lot, allowing you to expand your property even further.
